    <briefdescription>
<para>Object used by mdrun ranks to signal to each other at this step. </para>    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<internal><para>This object has responsibility to read signal values from <computeroutput>gs</computeroutput>, coordinate communication within and perhaps between simulations, and set result signal values in <computeroutput>gs</computeroutput> as appropriate.</para><para>It is intended to have a very short lifetime, so should remain easy to construct and destruct on the stack just when the global communication occurs. </para></internal>
    </detaileddescription>
